ON SELECTION BAR 13 OF actualizac do form frmprestadq
ON SELECTION BAR 14 OF actualizac do form frmquirof10 with 3
ON SELECTION BAR 16 OF actualizac do form frmpreqx11
ON SELECTION BAR 17 OF actualizac do form frmquirof30

